Hereâ€™s a comprehensive list of all CSS Grid properties and their possible values:

--------------------------------------------

1. Grid Container Properties

---------------------------------------------------

1. display : grid;
2. display : inline-grid;

------------------------------------------------

1. grid-template-columns : Length values (100px, 20%, etc.)
2. grid-template-columns : Fractional units (1fr, 2fr, etc.)
3. grid-template-columns : repeat()
4. grid-template-columns : minmax(min, max)
5. grid-template-columns : auto-fill
6. grid-template-columns : auto-fit
7. grid-template-columns : none (default)

-----------------------------------------------
1. grid-template-rows : Length values (100px, 20%, etc.)
2. grid-template-rows : Fractional units (1fr, 2fr, etc.)
3. grid-template-rows : repeat()
4. grid-template-rows : minmax(min, max)
5. grid-template-rows : none (default)

-------------------------------------------------

1. grid-template-areas : 'area-name' (e.g., 'header header header')
2. grid-template-areas : . (empty cell)

-----------------------------------------------

1. grid-template : Combine grid-template-rows / grid-template-columns / grid-template-areas.

------------------------------------------------

1. grid-column-gap (Deprecated: use column-gap) : Length values (10px, 1em, etc.)

------------------------------------------------

1. grid-row-gap (Deprecated: use row-gap) : Length values (10px, 1em, etc.)

--------------------------------------------------

1. grid-gap (Deprecated: use gap) : Length values (10px, 1em, etc.)

----------------------------------------------------
1. gap : row-gap column-gap

---------------------------------------------------

1. grid-auto-rows : Length values (100px, auto, minmax(min, max))

--------------------------------------------------

1. grid-auto-columns : Length values (100px, auto, minmax(min, max))

--------------------------------------------------

1. grid-auto-flow : row (default)
2. grid-auto-flow : column
3. grid-auto-flow : dense
4. grid-auto-flow : row dense
5. grid-auto-flow : column dense

-------------------------------------------------

1. align-items : start
2. align-items : end
3. align-items : center
4. align-items : stretch (default)

--------------------------------------------

1. justify-items : start
2. justify-items : end
3. justify-items : center
4. justify-items : stretch (default)

-------------------------------------------

1. place-items : align-items justify-items

------------------------------------------

1. align-content : start
2. align-content : end
3. align-content : center
4. align-content : stretch (default)
5. align-content : space-between
6. align-content : space-around
7. align-content : space-evenly

------------------------------------------

1. justify-content : start
2. justify-content : end
3. justify-content : center
4. justify-content : stretch (default)
5. justify-content : space-between
6. justify-content : space-around
7. justify-content : space-evenly

------------------------------------------

1. place-content : align-content justify-content

------------------------------------------

2. Grid Item Properties

-----------------------------------------

1. grid-column-start : Grid line number (1, 2, etc.)
2. grid-column-start : Named grid line
3. grid-column-start : span n (span across n columns)
4. grid-column-start : auto

-----------------------------------------

1. grid-column-end : Grid line number (1, 2, etc.)
2. grid-column-end : Named grid line
3. grid-column-end : span n (span across n columns)
4. grid-column-end : auto

----------------------------------------

1. grid-row-start : Grid line number (1, 2, etc.)
2. grid-row-start : Named grid line
3. grid-row-start : span n (span across n rows)
4. grid-row-start : auto

----------------------------------------

1. grid-row-end : Grid line number (1, 2, etc.)
2. grid-row-end : Named grid line
3. grid-row-end : span n (span across n rows)
4. grid-row-end : auto

----------------------------------------

1. grid-column : start-line / end-line

------------------------------------------

1. grid-row : start-line / end-line

----------------------------------------

1. grid-area : grid-row-start / grid-column-start / grid-row-end / grid-column-end
2. grid-area : Area name (if grid-template-areas is defined)

----------------------------------------

1. align-self : start
2. align-self : end
3. align-self : center
4. align-self : stretch (default)

-------------------------------------

1. justify-self : start
2. justify-self : end
3. justify-self : center
4. justify-self : stretch (default)

-------------------------------------

1. place-self : align-self justify-self

------------------------------------------

3. Grid Template Functions

----------------------------------

a. repeat()
Repeats a column or row definition.

Example: repeat(3, 1fr)
b. minmax()
Defines a range for the size of a grid track.

Example: minmax(100px, 1fr)
c. auto-fill
Automatically fills the grid with as many tracks as possible.

Example: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(100px, 1fr))
d. auto-fit
Similar to auto-fill, but collapses empty tracks.

Example: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(100px, 1fr))








